{
  "stem": "27150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were poets, and there were painters, and there were writers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, mostly, you see, during the school times, you see, we belonged to an organization.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would see that just like, you see, Poles didn't like the Jews, and Jews didn't like the Poles-- so among the Jews, the religious ones, the orthodox, didn't like the progressive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The progressive didn't like orthodox.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, among the progressive, you see, there were Zionists, and there were Bundist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, we subscribed to Hashomer Hatzair that were left-- Zionists, you see, labor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, we were attending meetings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Robak ?] and I, we were in a special group that spoke Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other, you see, sort of platoons, or some-- There was a platoon, and there was a [INAUDIBLE] We started as, you see, sort of sparrows-- the group of sparrows, and then we got, got promoted to cubs.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were having discussions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About Israel, about Jews, about history.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now, there was a Jewish holiday called Lag B'Omer, and so we went to excursions, and we had sort of Purim concerts, all the six Tarbut schools had the circus.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a choir, and there was aerobics, gymnastics, and all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was sitting behind the choir and just, on a very low voice, you see, repeated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now, when there was Lag B'Omer, we used to go, you see, by steamship, you see, to the-- to a place more up the river to [INAUDIBLE] and put tents, and play the bow and arrow-- most kids do.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was sort of scouts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eh, it wasn't crystallized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sort of-- I felt very well, and I felt all right in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
